### 6. Choosing the correct `contentConfig`

| Scenario                     | `contentConfig.type` | Example blocks                                                                                                   |
| --------------------------- | -------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Displays **multiple** items | `ans-feed`           | card-list-block, numbered-list-block, results-list-block, search-results-list-block, simple-list-block, top-table-list-block |
| Displays **single** item    | `ans-item`           | extra-large-promo-block, large-promo-block, medium-promo-block, small-promo-block                                  |
